{"word":"ἡμερίς","slug":"ἡμερίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἡμερίς</b></el> <el>(ἡμερίς, ίδος) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> of <a href='S:ἥμερος'><el>ἥμερος</el></a>\n<p/>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>ἡμερίς</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>ἄμπελος</el>), <i>the cultivated vine</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>ἀγριάς</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: but distinguished from <a href='S:ἀμπελίς'><el>ἀμπελίς</el></a> by <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}